{"tid":1608660,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔好自行起開槍狗底 要逼狗隊同佢公開割蓆","createTime":"2019-10-01T11:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T11:38:20.000Z","uid":6435,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"37825aebe2471752b9bbd28f87b349b775f81582","tid":1608660,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:13:56.000Z","msg":"老豆搵仔<br />\n你地都戇鳩<br />\n咪撚再亂傳開槍黑警嘅流料<br />\n啲料傳得咁快睇來班曱甴真係好驚，渣渣聲推個人出嚟承擔責任就算<br />\n你班曱甴想鬆人？發夢都冇咁早<br />\n我哋正式宣布，搵到開槍狗都唔會出<br />\n三萬警犬共榮辱<br />\n全部都係殺人犯<br />\n狗仔全部都係殺人犯之子<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要逼到班狗主動公開同開槍狗割蓆<br />\n佢唔割就逼到成隊狗隊連九族一齊攬炒</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6f88c6792ae7d86164e16e78ff254f11a877f45d","tid":1608660,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:14:26.000Z","msg":"用下腦都知啦<br />\n邊會咁易起到<br />\n擺到明對家放條友出黎受死"},{"pid":"69d1b5f27d18d4cc2da1bf1c0d553ae06287f136","tid":1608660,"uid":57633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21f067a6c29e320d2a6290175de0f9af8e2b5c7","tid":1608660,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478d4b5a6f769a292e3deeb7fd0124847014a7ec","tid":1608660,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"杜威係流料"},{"pid":"6292c6237bb6859001e38a86583a07a24ce2e9da","tid":1608660,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f88c6792ae7d86164e16e78ff254f11a877f45d","tid":1608660,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:14:26.000Z","msg":"用下腦都知啦<br />\n邊會咁易起到<br />\n擺到明對家放條友出黎受死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:18:19.000Z","msg":"邊有可能咁撚快<br />\n擺明求其隊條友出黎受靶"},{"pid":"48edb1d74353903d236e07389df6c085127c0dca","t